<title>USA: Lanoptics holders approve stock buyback.</title>
<headline>Lanoptics holders approve stock buyback.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-06-12</dateline>
<text>
<p>LanOptics Ltd said Thursday that stockholders approved a proposal allowing the company to buy back up to 10 percent of its ordinary shares.</p>
<p>LanOptics recently gained approval from the District Court in Tel-Aviv to become the first Israeli company to repurchase its shares.</p>
<p>The company has 6.1 million ordinary shares outstanding.</p>
